highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 152 days straight.
DPR IAN has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Nerves” is the highest at #15.
“No Room For A Saint (From F1® The Movie)” by Dom Dolla, Nathan Nicholson, and F1 The Album is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #98.
“Bad As I Used To Be (From F1® The Movie)” by Chris Stapleton and F1 The Album is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 25 spots at #65.
